WEBVTT

00:08:30.720 --> 00:08:33.816
Now, that was a painful realization for me

00:08:33.840 --> 00:08:35.976
and made me realize,

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:38.296
if we want to change this,

00:08:38.320 --> 00:08:40.679
we need to engage,
and we need to do better.

00:08:42.200 --> 00:08:44.560
Now, what to do?

00:08:45.320 --> 00:08:48.856
Achieving more than 20 percent
women in leadership

00:08:48.880 --> 00:08:51.256
seems like a daunting task to many,

00:08:51.280 --> 00:08:53.760
understandably, given the track record.

00:08:55.080 --> 00:08:56.296
But it's doable,

00:08:56.320 --> 00:08:59.576
and there are many companies today
that are making progress there

00:08:59.600 --> 00:09:01.216
and doing it successfully.